1
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,439
What are you doing?

2
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:47,359
Don't forget.

3
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:49,119
You're my fiancée now.

4
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:50,000
Don't you forget, either.

5
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:50,960
You promised me.

6
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,399
I'll play your fiancée perfectly.

7
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:54,359
You have to convince your father to let Zhang Xiaobei go.

8
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,880
You care that much about Zhang Xiaobei?

9
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:01,479
Think about the Lin family.

10
00:01:02,479 --> 00:01:03,960
Without Prosperity Group's funding,

11
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,359
your hospital would've been ruined long ago.

12
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:07,439
For him,

13
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,120
is it worth it?

14
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,319
In my father's will,

15
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:21,200
is there a designated heir?

16
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,239
I'm sorry.

17
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,879
About Chairman Sheng's will,

18
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,560
I can't discuss that with you here.

19
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:31,120
By the way, the document I asked you to sign last time,

20
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,879
the Supplemental Agreement for the AI project.

21
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:35,040
Bring it to my office tomorrow.

22
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:36,359
Well...

23
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,439
You know,

24
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,640
Chairman Sheng sent me to find Zhang Xiaobei

25
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,079
to sign the Supplemental Agreement.

26
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:43,920
Yes.

27
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,280
The chairman already told me.

28
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:47,519
From now on, I'm fully in charge of this project.

29
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,920
I want all the files for this project.

30
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,359
Understood.

31
00:01:51,879 --> 00:01:53,000
I'll have someone deliver it tomorrow.

32
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,400
Thank you, Lawyer He.

33
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,120
Don't bother my father with these minor things.

34
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,760
If anything comes up,

35
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:01,640
just come to me directly.

36
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:02,519
Goodbye.

37
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,680
So forcing me to transfer the patent...

38
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,280
was ordered by Sheng Shizhong.

39
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,280
And Sheng Yuanzhou didn't even know.

40
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:15,120
His own son isn't the heir.

41
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:19,560
This father-son relationship is anything but normal.

42
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,639
This way, please.

43
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,120
Miss Lin.

44
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,680
These are all our new seasonal arrivals.

45
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,400
Take a look.

46
00:02:31,159 --> 00:02:32,319
I'm fine with anything. You pick.

47
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:36,439
Then we'll take one of each style.

48
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,039
Mr. Sheng is really good to his fiancée.

49
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:41,000
He's just going through the motions.

50
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,000
I'm just a trophy.

51
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,240
How could that be?

52
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,280
In your eyes,

53
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:46,719
isn't it just how much he spends on you

54
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:47,759
that shows how much he loves you?

55
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,280
A man's love for a woman

56
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,439
isn't the amount of money he spends,

57
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:52,560
it's the proportion he's willing to spend.

58
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:54,639
These clothes are nothing to you.

59
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,719
So your love

60
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,240
is worthless.

61
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,199
Why don't you try this one?

62
00:02:59,199 --> 00:03:00,080
It just came in yesterday.

63
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:00,520
Let's go.

64
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:01,479
This way, please.

65
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,800
Money sure is nice.

66
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:54,280
It can buy respect and envy,

67
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,879
even love.

68
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,960
Don't you think you look pathetic,

69
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:04,439
propping yourself up with money?

70
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,360
Not at all.

71
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,479
I'm very happy.

72
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,719
But you...

73
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,960
Acting all high and mighty makes me sick.

74
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:33,160
Siqi.

75
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,879
What are you doing here?

76
00:04:35,879 --> 00:04:37,279
This dress is so pretty.

77
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,560
Looks like your big day is coming soon.

78
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,759
Stop making fun of me.

79
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:46,920
I've got enough on my mind.

80
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,360
Others would kill to be in your shoes.

81
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,279
And you're saying you're annoyed?

82
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,480
If you like it,

83
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:51,519
take it.

84
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,639
Then I'll really take it.

85
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:04,439
Just kidding.

86
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,560
I'm going to try on the gown first.

87
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,279
See you in a bit.

88
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,920
Isn't that Siqi's bestie?

89
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,480
Why is she acting like that toward me?

90
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,879
Could it be Sheng Yuanzhou and her...

91
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,160
Hello.

92
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:01,480
What are you doing here?

93
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,920
Mr. Sheng, you're really good at putting up with things.

94
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,879
A woman who made you a cuckold,

95
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:09,319
and you'll still willingly get engaged and marry her.

96
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:11,720
That's my business.

97
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:13,199
Who are you to question it?

98
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,839
Given our relationship,

99
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,560
I can at least complain a little, can't I?

100
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:23,439
I just think you're a poor thing.

101
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,000
Miss Lin.

102
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,160
Please take a look at these styles.

103
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,759
Especially this one,

104
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:32,759
and the one you just tried on...

105
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,079
Lin Siqi.

106
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,680
I'm going to show you

107
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,959
how ugly the man you chose really is.

108
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:39,279
Fine.

109
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,680
I'd love to see it.

110
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,839
How exactly do you comfort a "poor thing"?

111
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:51,560
Treating your friend's fiancé like this...

112
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,480
do you think that's appropriate?

113
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:55,800
Didn't you call me cheap?

114
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,040
What do I have left to care about?

115
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,240
Do you see it?

116
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:11,519
This is the man you chose.

117
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:21,160
Miss Lin,

118
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,079
your fiancé is cheating with your bestie.

119
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,759
Siqi, seeing all this,

120
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,720
must be devastated, right?

121
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,560
This is hilarious.

122
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:46,399
Stay away from Siqi from now on.

123
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,360
If you dare hurt her,

124
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,600
don't blame me if I get rough with you.

125
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:05,120
Excuse me, coming through.

126
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:06,839
Xiaobei.

127
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:11,120
Siqi.

128
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,240
What's wrong?

129
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,079
I...

130
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:17,959
Let's go, hurry.

131
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,040
Is something going on?

132
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:21,920
I'm fine.

133
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:24,279
Go on. You're going to run out of time.

134
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:28,639
Hello?

135
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,759
I'm just one intersection away.

136
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:30,319
I'll be there in a minute.

137
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:32,240
I'm starving to death waiting here.

138
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,440
Go feed it to the dogs.

139
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,279
I'm definitely filing a complaint.

140
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,559
Give it to me. I'll have it for dinner.

141
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,399
But...

142
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,440
It's what someone else didn't want.

143
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,000
So what?

144
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:53,799
Didn't we used to

145
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:55,440
eat canceled orders all the time?

146
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:57,039
Well...

147
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,320
that doesn't seem right, does it?

148
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:04,879
Xiaobei.

149
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:07,039
That day...

150
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:10,240
I'm sorry.

151
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:28,919
You don't need to apologize to me.

152
00:09:30,879 --> 00:09:31,759
I believe you.

153
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,200
You must have had your reasons.

154
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,240
You didn't mean to hurt me.

155
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,480
You don't have to worry about me.

156
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:43,799
Think more about yourself.

157
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,039
Xiaobei.

158
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:23,799
What are you doing?

159
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:34,519
Sheng Yuanzhou.

160
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,679
Since you don't even like me,

161
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:37,759
and you know I don't like you either,

162
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,360
why do you have to do this?

163
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:40,440
Sheng Yuanzhou.

164
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:42,480
Siqi isn't your property.

165
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:46,919
Sheng Yuanzhou.

166
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,679
Siqi, she's not your property.

167
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:52,360
She has the right to choose who she loves.

168
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,519
Who are you to say that?

169
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,039
You impostor.

170
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,080
Sheng Yuanzhou.

171
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,720
Can't you just let me go?

172
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:04,919
You know that

173
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:05,519
I agreed to the engagement

174
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:07,039
for Xiaobei and my family.

175
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,320
I can stick to the deal

176
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,360
and play a good wife,

177
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:10,960
staying by your side.

178
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,720
But even if I'm with you,

179
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,519
my heart and my mind

180
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:15,639
will only belong to Zhang Xiaobei.

181
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,279
Can you really live like that?

182
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:26,240
So everything you did was for

183
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:30,480
him?

184
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,480
You knew it all along,

185
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,120
how important Zhang Xiaobei is to me.

186
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,960
So why keep forcing me to stay?

187
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,120
You're right.

188
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:44,360
Money can buy a lot of things,

189
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,240
but it can't buy a sincere heart.

190
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,440
So I won't hurt the one I truly love anymore.

191
00:11:51,159 --> 00:11:51,720
I'm sorry.

192
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:05,080
Siqi made a deal for my sake,

193
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,639
so she had to get engaged to Sheng Yuanzhou.

194
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:10,879
Siqi.

195
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:12,840
I'm sorry.

196
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:20,759
What you just said...

197
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,840
Stop it, it's really embarrassing.

198
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:26,679
Fine, I won't say it.

199
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:28,399
But...

200
00:12:29,639 --> 00:12:30,639
I've taken it all to heart.

201
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,399
It's getting late.

202
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:37,720
I'm going home.

203
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:40,159
Okay, I'll call you a car.

204
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:42,720
We'll do it the usual way.

205
00:12:42,879 --> 00:12:43,919
Just give me a ride on your bike.

206
00:12:50,399 --> 00:12:51,639
You sure?

207
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,639
I used to give you rides on my bike?

208
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:54,679
Of course.

209
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,440
I kinda remember that.

210
00:13:01,919 --> 00:13:04,519
But why does it feel so unfamiliar?

211
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:13,720
Come on.

212
00:13:35,159 --> 00:13:35,480
Again.

213
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:41,840
So you liked Siqi all along too.

214
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,879
But sorry, Sheng Yuanzhou.

215
00:14:45,639 --> 00:14:47,080
Siqi loves me.

216
00:14:58,559 --> 00:14:59,799
Before it's too late,

217
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:02,759
I'll end your engagement to Siqi, no matter what.

218
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:09,679
Still like a little kid.

219
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,320
Every time it's my birthday,

220
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,720
you always want cake from the hotel.

221
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,000
Siqi.

222
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:18,320
You're grown up now, getting married.

223
00:15:18,799 --> 00:15:20,120
Dad, it's your birthday today.

224
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,039
Why are you saying that?

225
00:15:21,039 --> 00:15:22,519
Come on, Dad, let's buy a strawberry cake.

226
00:15:22,519 --> 00:15:23,480
It's a limited edition.

227
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,600
Where are we going later?

